v1.2 - 3/26/2024



- The Post-night minigame can now be replayable in the Minigames section of the extras.


- Resized the hitbox for the player in the post-night minigame.


- Night 5 has been rebalanced a bit.


- New game will no longer reset your entire save data.


- You can now hold DEL to reset your entire save data.
